Entry.JapaneseText: <Tytree>って、本当に セレーナさんに弱いよネ！
Entry.EnglishText: You sure have a weak spot for Selena, <Tytree>!

Entry.JapaneseText: <Mao>、やけに姉貴の事でつっかかってくるな。 わかった、おまえも兄弟が欲しいんだな？
Entry.EnglishText: <Mao>, you're always ragging on me about my sister... I get it, you want a sibling of your own, right?

Entry.JapaneseText: 仕方がない、おれがアニキになってやる。 姉は<Annie>でガマンしてくれ。
Entry.EnglishText: Guess it can't be helped, I'll have to be your older brother. You'll have to make do with <Annie> as your older sister.
